# Build Configuration Guide

The project uses Gradle for build management. Key configuration details are in [build.gradle](mdc:build.gradle).

## Project Details
- Group: `edu.careflow`
- Version: `1.0-SNAPSHOT`
- Java Version: 21
- Main Module: `edu.careflow`
- Main Class: `edu.careflow.Careflow`

## Key Plugins
- JavaFX Plugin (version 21)
- Java Modularity Plugin
- JLink Plugin for creating custom runtime images

## Main Dependencies
- JavaFX Modules:
  - javafx.controls
  - javafx.fxml
  - javafx.swing
  - javafx.web

- Database:
  - MySQL Connector/J (8.3.0)
  - SQLite JDBC (3.43.2.0)

- UI Components:
  - GemsFX (2.103.0)
  - ControlsFX (11.2.0)
  - CalendarFX (11.12.7)
  - Ikonli FontAwesome5 Pack

- Excel Support:
  - Apache POI (5.2.5)
  - Apache Commons Collections
  - Apache Commons IO
  - Apache Commons Math
  - XMLBeans

## Build Features
- UTF-8 encoding for all Java compilations
- JUnit 5 for testing
- Custom JVM arguments for Apache POI
- JLink configuration for creating optimized runtime images

